{"tid":2234760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年10月尾示威3男女涉管有胡椒噴劑金屬棒 事隔近一年被起訴 15歲被告被捕後到在警車上曾多次被警員襲擊","createTime":"2020-10-08T06:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T06:52:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8fc47a037dda232ba53381fe9b99c7ad6c23fa9","tid":2234760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4029&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5CaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=07df45e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4029</a><br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】去年10月尾示威活動期間，2男1女涉在深水埗管有胡椒噴劑、噴漆和金屬棒等被控，今早分2案於西九龍裁判法院首次提堂。案件分別押後至11月19日和12月3日再訊，以待辯方索取檢控文件和法律意見。3名被告獲准以2000元保釋外出，期間不得離港，須交出旅遊證件，居於報稱住址，每星期到警署報到1次，並遵守宵禁令和深水埗一帶禁足令。辯方於庭上透露15歲被告被捕後到在警車上，曾多次被警員襲擊，致頭部受傷，當晚需留醫觀察。（全文 (<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1892453/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-3%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E6%B6%89%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%99%B4%E5%8A%91%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E6%A3%92-%E5%88%862%E6%A1%88%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E8%A8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1892453%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-3%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E5%2599%25B4%25E5%258A%2591%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%25A3%2592-%25E5%2588%25862%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25A8%258A&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5CaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=92906838\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1892453%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6